Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Like a distant dream in a realm that is lost in wonder
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Day after day, I'm searching for the meaning
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,But the only sign is locked deep inside of you
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Memories waning as the night grows long
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,And the voice grows strong
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Who am I and where do I belong?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,現世へ続く道　行け
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,闇夜に燃ゆる星よ月よ　真実の灯よ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,胸に秘めし想い　照らし出せ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,声を上げ　八千代に願い馳せ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,恐れも迷いも哀しみも乗り越え
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,天上天下響くまで
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,共に時を刻みし者よ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,永遠の夢を紡ぎし友よ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,Because of you I know now there's only one way
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,To escape the truth or to face the new day
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,If there's only one way, I will face the new day
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,I will face the day with you
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,この身を包み込むは
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,常世の風
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,今、時を超え　千里の道を超え
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,願いも誓いも魂も抱いて
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,天上天下届くまで
Comment: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
